{"tid":2478432,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"馬恩國：香港市民夠多反政府，老師夠多黃絲","createTime":"2021-04-07T05:08:48.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-07T05:29:14.000Z","uid":5195,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f67c1266db8ca0b079bf41033627711db030e195","tid":2478432,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T05:08:48.000Z","msg":"【明報專訊】民建聯立法會議員葛珮帆（EQ）近年經常評論司法界、法律界，噚日佢喺報章撰文，批評香港大律師公會「屢為反中亂港者吶喊助威，挑戰『一國兩制』憲制權力」，仲話保留「大律師」係毫無必要，分大律師同律師嘅制度已不合時宜。<br />\n<br />\n馬：香港市民夠多反政府<br />\n<br />\n係咪踢晒佢哋落海？<br />\n<br />\nEQ黨友、身為大律師嘅香港法學交流基金會主席馬恩國好激動咁話，EQ連律師都未做過，對大律師業務一知半解，「司法嘅嘢關佢咩事？佢IT界㗎嘛」；反問如果因為大律師多「黃絲」就要消滅佢，「老師夠多黃絲，你係咪炒晒佢？香港市民夠多反政府，係咪踢晒佢哋落海？」"},{"pid":"dddc14dd89713325c3868dcb54cc8b25bc7d92bf","tid":2478432,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T05:09:47.000Z","msg":"又話藍絲係沉默大多數!?"},{"pid":"540cd22cf55b0015647586d82e7746df2ebbf1bd","tid":2478432,"uid":53687,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T05:09:48.000Z","msg":"馬生已犯國安法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b290b50b20a102a57f1c730e32b19b78ff5bd93","tid":2478432,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T05:10:54.000Z","msg":"鬥紅<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c0fa97296fa0b65f372c90ef4be1b20d069ce05","tid":2478432,"uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T05:11:46.000Z","msg":"澳洲人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"604affffc042963a667a0dad9c20474515b73126","tid":2478432,"uid":287247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T05:14:09.000Z","msg":"You are not a bloody Chinese<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e6bca9969a80831f3e15a4c2ea580b422c8eb95","tid":2478432,"uid":288675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T05:19:52.000Z","msg":"其實佢知唔知咩係大律師...唔好似為律師